{
  "texts": [
    "We did not find any significant interaction between source of reappraisal (GPT or human) and the type of emotions.",
    "We also did not find any difference in the quality of reappraisal as a function of emotion within humans and within GPT (see Supplemental Materials for detailed results).",
    "To get a better sense of the differences between humans and GPT-4 was looked at the percentile location of GPT-4 compared to humans.",
    "We first calculated the simple average of the four ratings (effectiveness, empathy, novelty, specificity) of each reappraisal.",
    "Next, for each vignette, we subset the data so that it only included a single GPT reappraisal alongside the rest of the human reappraisals."
  ]
}